https://github.com/brainupdaters/drlm
https://github.com/brainupdaters/fosdem17_workshop

ReaR over the network (PXE or NFS), so you don't have to use a USB stick or like
written in bash also

uses nfs, ssh, https, tftp, dhcp, drlm store

no GUI

Integration with system monitoring tools
- email
- zabbix
- nagios
- hp openview

Supports Debian, RedHat, Suse, Ubuntu

has a job scheduler (plan backups)

export and import DR images between DRLM servers (possibly on different sites)



